            "public_access_description": "This sword once belonged to the Iranian ruler Shah Tahmasp. Many of the finest works of Islamic art were created during his long reign (1524\u201376). The blade of the sword is inlaid in gold with Arabic lettering. The inscription includes Shah Tahmasp's titles and genealogy, as well as quotes from the Koran.", 
